NOTES: This district consists of two subdistricts, RES-25 and RES-10, which will be listed as alternatives in that order for the following dimensional standards.
This district has 3 classes: (1) Municipal sewer and municipal or public water (2) Municipal sewer and individual water (3) Individual sewer and individual, municipal, or public water

All uses and structures shall be subject to flood hazard review as well as all other applicable municipal and state regulations (but does not require a public hearing) except agriculture and forestry, unimproved open space and recreational/ educational uses.
